text: "Come See About Me" is a 1964 song by The Supremes. Come See About Me may also refer to: * Come See About Me (Neil Sedaka album) (1983) * Come See About Me (Freda Payne album) (2000) * Come See About Me (DVD), a 2004 concert film by John Lee Hooker * "Come See About Me", a 2019 song by Nicki Minaj from Queen
